{"title":"数据结构代码实现：交换类排序","uid":"1fc761e7ae44a5de58caea7dfaaa66ef","slug":"DataStructure-ExchangeSort","date":"2020-06-05T03:41:52.000Z","updated":"2020-06-06T05:25:04.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-ExchangeSort.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"冒泡排序\"><a href=\"#冒泡排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"冒泡排序\"></a>冒泡排序</h2><p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200606132336.png\" alt=\"冒泡排序\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void BubbleSort(ElemType A[],int n)&#123;\n    int i,j;\n    bool flag;&#x2F;&#x2F;表示本趟冒泡是否发生交换的标志\n    for(i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n-1;i++)&#123;\n        flag&#x3D; false;\n        for(j&#x3D;n-1;j&gt;i;j--)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;一趟冒泡过程\n            if(A[j-1]&gt;A[j])&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;若为逆序\n                swap(A[j-1],A[j]);&#x2F;&#x2F;交换\n                flag&#x3D;true;\n            &#125;\n        &#125;\n        if(!flag)&#123;\n            return;&#x2F;&#x2F;本趟遍历后没有发生交换，说明表已经有序\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"快速排序\"><a href=\"#快速排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"快速排序\"></a>快速排序</h2><p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200606132332.png\" alt=\"快速排序\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void QuickSort(ElemType A[],int low,int high)&#123;\n    if(low&lt;high)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;递归跳出条件\n        int pivotpos&#x3D;Partition(A,low,high);&#x2F;&#x2F;划分\n        QuickSort(A,low,pivotpos-1);&#x2F;&#x2F;依次对两个子表进行递归排序\n        QuickSort(A,pivotpos+1,high);\n\n    &#125;         \n&#125;\n\nint Partition(ElemType A[], int low, int high) &#123;\n    ElemType pivot&#x3D;A[low];&#x2F;&#x2F;将当前表中的第一个元素设置为枢轴值，对表进行划分\n    while(low&lt;high)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;循环跳出条件\n        while(low&lt;high&amp;&amp;A[high]&gt;&#x3D;pivot)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;\n            --high;\n        &#125;\n        A[low]&#x3D;A[high];&#x2F;&#x2F;将比枢轴值小的元素移动到左端\n        while (low&lt;high&amp;&amp;A[low]&lt;&#x3D;pivot)&#123;\n            ++low;\n        &#125;\n        A[high]&#x3D;A[low];&#x2F;&#x2F;将比枢轴值大的元素移动到右端\n    &#125;\n    A[low]&#x3D;pivot;&#x2F;&#x2F;枢轴元素存放到最终位置\n    return low;&#x2F;&#x2F;返回存放枢轴的最终位置\n&#125;</code></pre>","feature":true,"text":"冒泡排序 void BubbleSort(ElemType A[],int n)&#123; int i,j; bool flag;&#x2F;&#x2F;表示本趟冒泡是否发生交换的标志 for(i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n-1;i++)&#123; flag&#x3D; fa...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%86%92%E6%B3%A1%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">冒泡排序</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">快速排序</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"SpringBoot：mybatisPlus整合","uid":"e55f38e7bc396b6c7c85ed555aed0683","slug":"SpringBoot-mybatis","date":"2021-02-07T11:44:16.000Z","updated":"2021-02-07T11:50:24.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/SpringBoot-mybatis.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/1502093784622523.png","text":"整合Mybatis 导入mybatis官方starter编写mapper接口。标注@Mapper注解编写sql映射文件并绑定mapper接口（或者不用sql映射文件，直接用注解）在application.yaml中指定Mapper配置文件的位置，以及指定